questions.quote: So. I just thought the two of us should hang out for a bit. I mean, you know, we've never really talked. I guess you'd know that, being one of the two of us, though, right?
Look, Rachel's told me how much easier you've made all this on her. Why can't you do that for me?
Honey, I'm not even going to pretend I was listening. Hey! Hey!
Oh god look at her sleeping. Oh, I love her so much! Oh, I think I'm gonna wake her up.
Yeah, I know. I hate it too. Look, maybe we should just tell them.
Somewhere there is someone with a tranquilizer gun and a huge butterfly net looking for that man.
Oh, I wish. Look, honey, you have that report to finish, and I gotta go see my lawyer.
Huuh, alright, Danny Arshak, ninth grade. Oh, c'mon Rach, you know the bottle was totally pointing at me.
Sometimes I wonder if I did the right thing, ya know, giving him away.
Yes. Yes! Fine! I am someone! You want me to say it? I have doubts! I'm sorry!
